Flow diagram: Agent Loop - Observe -> Plan -> Act -> Reflect -> (loop back to Plan). Four nodes in a cycle: 1) Observe: Input understanding (eye icon), 2) Plan: Decide next step (list icon), 3) Act: Tool execution (hammer icon), 4) Reflect: Evaluate result (checkmark icon). Arrow from Reflect back to Plan labeled 'Ziel nicht erreicht'. Arrow from Reflect to 'Finale Antwort' labeled 'Ziel erreicht'. Minimalist cycle diagram.